  "text": "Venus Optics, a leading manufacturer of professional camera lenses, is proud to release an interesting Wide-Angle Macro lens – the 15mm f/4.5 lens with a 0.5x magnification ratio. This capability allows the capture of stunning and unique wide-angle macro shots at a minimum focusing distance of 12.9cm, making every photo rich in detail at every distance. The combination of wide perspective and macro capability provides creators with a whole new world of opportunity for creative shots. The optical design is also optimized with excellent distortion control. Whether you are a wildlife photographer, architecture shooter, or other content creator, this lens is the perfect tool to create impactful visuals. The 15mm lens is crafted to be lightweight and compact, with 0.68lb/ 308g, making the lens easy to carry and use on the go. Laowa 15mm f/4.5 0.5X5Focal Length: 15mmAperture Range: F4.5-F32Angle of View: 110.5°Max. Magnification 1:2Full-FrameManual Focus16 Elements in 11 Groups Ultra-wide 15mm Perspective 0.5x Magnification Ratio (Close Focusing at 12.9cm) Excellent Distortion Control Compact \u0026 Lightweight Design (0.68lb/308g) Auto Aperture Available for E/Z/EF Mount 10-point Sunstar Well-built Lens Housing Removable Lens Hood 62mm Filter Thread Multiple mount options: EF/ F/ E / Z / RF / L mount Ultra-wide 15mm Perspective Laowa 15mm f/4.5 0.5X Wide Angle Macro features a 110.5° wide angle of view, resulting in a stunning and epic photo, particularly suitable for landscape \u0026 wildlife shots. ©Alberto Ghizzi Panizza ©Frank Leinz ©JiuChongGe 0.5x Macro with Great Close Focusing Capabilities (12.9cm) The 0.5x magnification ratio of this 15mm macro lens provides a practical range, allowing the capture of the subject in the foreground while including as much background info as possible for a powerful and unique shot. ©Alberto Ghizzi Panizza ©Alberto Ghizzi Panizza ©Gerry Caracas ©Frank Leinz ©Jimmy Cheng Excellent Distortion Control The 15mm lens is designed to keep distortion at a low level. Perfect for shooting architecture, landscape, or interior. ©Jimmy Cheng Compact \u0026 Lightweight Design (0.68lb/308g) With a lightweight design of 0.68lb / 308g (1.88”xØ2.76” / 47.7mm*Ø70mm), the overall size is remarkably compact for capturing awesome shots on the go. 10-point Sunstar The 15mm macro lens features 5 aperture blades, resulting in a 10-point sunstar for a unique aesthetic. ©Alberto Ghizzi Panizza Auto Aperture (Available for E / Z / EF Mount) For Sony E, Nikon Z, and Canon EF camera users, the aperture can be adjusted directly from the camera. The electronic chip also allows the recording of metadata in EXIF. Well-built Lens Housing The 15mm lens is designed to provide a smooth photo shooting experience. Pricing \u0026 Availability Laowa 15mm f/4.5 0.5X Wide Angle Macro is available for purchase at Venus Optics direct. Laowa 15mm f/4.5 0.5X5Focal Length: 15mmAperture Range: F4.5-F32Angle of View: 110.5°Max. Magnification 1:2Full-FrameManual Focus16 Elements in 11 Groups Product Gallery When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission. Here's how it works. Go to discussion...",
  "image": "https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/laowa1545macro169.jpg",
  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003carticle id=\"post-67752\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eVenus Optics, a leading manufacturer of professional camera lenses, is proud to release an interesting \u003ca href=\"https://www.venuslens.net/product/laowa-15mm-f-4-5-0-5x-wide-angle-macro/ref/1112/\"\u003eWide-Angle Macro lens – the 15mm f/4.5 lens with a \u003cstrong\u003e0.5x magnification ratio\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis capability allows the capture of stunning and unique wide-angle macro shots at a \u003cstrong\u003eminimum focusing distance of 12.9cm\u003c/strong\u003e, making every photo rich in detail at every distance.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003ecombination of wide perspective and macro\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ecapability\u003c/strong\u003e provides creators with a whole new world of opportunity for creative shots. The optical design is also optimized with \u003cstrong\u003eexcellent distortion control\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhether you are a wildlife photographer, architecture shooter, or other content creator, this lens is the perfect tool to create impactful visuals. The 15mm lens is crafted to be \u003cstrong\u003elightweight and compact, \u003c/strong\u003ewith 0.68lb/ 308g, making the lens easy to carry and use on the go.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eLaowa 15mm f/4.5 0.5X\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.venuslens.net/product/laowa-15mm-f-4-5-0-5x-wide-angle-macro/ref/1112/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-post-title=\"Laowa 15mm f/4.5 0.5X\" data-aff-link=\"https://www.venuslens.net/product/laowa-15mm-f-4-5-0-5x-wide-angle-macro/ref/1112/\" data-post-type=\"box\" data-post-id=\"301789\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/laowa1545mc.jpg\" alt=\"Laowa 15mm f/4.5 0.5X\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e5\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-selenium=\"sellingPointsListItem\"\u003eFocal Length: 15mm\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-selenium=\"sellingPointsListItem\"\u003eAperture Range: F4.5-F32\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-selenium=\"sellingPointsListItem\"\u003eAngle of View: 110.5°\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-selenium=\"sellingPointsListItem\"\u003eMax. Magnification 1:2\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-selenium=\"sellingPointsListItem\"\u003eFull-Frame\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-selenium=\"sellingPointsListItem\"\u003eManual Focus\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-selenium=\"sellingPointsListItem\"\u003e16 Elements in 11 Groups\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUltra-wide 15mm Perspective\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e0.5x Magnification Ratio (Close Focusing at 12.9cm)\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eExcellent Distortion Control\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eCompact \u0026amp; Lightweight Design (0.68lb/308g)\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eAuto Aperture Available for E/Z/EF Mount\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e10-point Sunstar\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eWell-built Lens Housing\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRemovable Lens Hood\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e62mm Filter Thread\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eMultiple mount options: EF/ F/ E / Z / RF / L mount\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1430\" height=\"954\" src=\"https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-5.jpeg 1430w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-5-728x486.jpeg 728w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-5-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-5-150x100.jpeg 150w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-5-450x300.jpeg 450w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-5-1200x801.jpeg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1430px) 100vw, 1430px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"h-ultra-wide-15mm-perspective\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUltra-wide 15mm Perspective\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eLaowa 15mm f/4.5 0.5X Wide Angle Macro features a 110.5° wide angle of view, resulting in a stunning and epic photo, particularly suitable for landscape \u0026amp; wildlife shots.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1885\" height=\"1254\" src=\"https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-6.jpeg 1885w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-6-728x484.jpeg 728w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-6-768x511.jpeg 768w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-6-1536x1022.jpeg 1536w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-6-150x100.jpeg 150w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-6-450x299.jpeg 450w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-6-1200x798.jpeg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1885px) 100vw, 1885px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e©Alberto Ghizzi Panizza\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"1020\" data-id=\"67759\" src=\"https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-7.jpeg 680w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-7-383x575.jpeg 383w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-7-150x225.jpeg 150w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-7-450x675.jpeg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp\u003e©Frank Leinz\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"681\" height=\"1018\" data-id=\"67760\" src=\"https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-8.jpeg 681w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-8-385x575.jpeg 385w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-8-150x224.jpeg 150w, https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/word-image-67752-8-450x673.jpeg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 681px) 100vw, 681px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp\u003e©JiuChongGe\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"h-0-5x-macro-with-great-close-focusing-capabilities-12-9cm\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e0.5x Macro with Great Close Focusing Capabilities (12.9cm)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe 0.5x magnification ratio of this 15mm macro lens provides a practical range, allowing the capture of the subject in the foreground while including as much background info as possible for a powerful and unique shot.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1084\" height=\"721\" src=\"https://www.canonrumors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/a-butterfly-on-a-flower-ai-generated-content-may.jpeg\" alt=\"